@model MyPortfolioWebApp.Models.Board

@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "삭제 확인";
}

<section id="board" class="section">
    <div class="container section-title" data-aos="fade-up">
        <h2>자유게시판</h2>
        <p>자유롭게 의견을 나눌 수 있는 공간입니다</p>
    </div>

    <div class="container" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
        <h4>글 삭제</h4>
        <p>정말 이 글을 삭제하시겠습니까?</p>
        <hr />

        <dl class="row">
            <dt class="col-sm-2">작성자</dt>
            <dd class="col-sm-10">@Model.Writer (@Model.Email)</dd>

            <dt class="col-sm-2">제목</dt>
            <dd class="col-sm-10">@Model.Title</dd>

            <dt class="col-sm-2">내용</dt>
            <dd class="col-sm-10">@Model.Contents</dd>

            <dt class="col-sm-2">작성일</dt>
            <dd class="col-sm-10">@Model.PostDate?.ToString("yyyy-MM-dd")</dd>
        </dl>

        <form asp-action="Delete">
            <input type="hidden" asp-for="Id" />
            <input type="submit" value="삭제" class="btn btn-sm btn-danger" />
            <a asp-action="Index" class="btn btn-sm btn-secondary">취소</a>
        </form>
    </div>
</section>
